// https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XfXcRN sphere pair tangent cone, by 2024 jt
// rotated 3d version of https://www.shadertoy.com/view/XcfyzH circle pair tangent

// Calculating the tangent cone to a pair of spheres.
// (no tangent if one spheres contains the other)

// tags: sphere, tangent, pair, cone

